Please enable \"Display pop-up windows while running in the background\". Without this enabled, \"Force stop applications\" will not be working.

Permission for event parameter \"SMS/MMS sensor\" is not granted. Click this notification to open Extender. In it use button for grant this permission.

Notifications permission is not granted.\n\nPlease enable notifications for PhoneProfilesPlusExtender. Without this enabled, notifications from PhoneProfilesPlusExtender will not be displayed.
If is not possible to enable Accessibility service, maybe are not allowed restricted settings for PhoneProfilesPlusExtender.
Click \"App info\" button to allow it.
In \"App info\" screen, click menu at top and in it \"Allow restricted settings\".
\"Allow restricted settings\" is not displayed, when restricted settings are allowed.
However, if PhoneProfilesPlusExtender is installed from a downloaded apk file, \"Allow restricted settings\" may not appear at all.
Then you must uninstall it, and install it from supported store, for example Droid-ify.
